Greedy Algorithm : 
===================
	A greedy algorithm is a problem-solving approach that makes the best immediate or 
	locally optimal choice at each stage with the hope of finding a global optimum solution. 
	It focuses on making the most beneficial choice at the present moment without 
	considering the long-term consequences or potential impact on future decisions. 
	
